der why people are leading the charge about nerfing Buff Bots.<br>
<br>
BTW, let's not forget that it is stats like those that Danlitus had when he routinely owned infiltrators on Galahad and then people (including Danlitus himself) starting posting screenshots of Doublefrost that were off the charts, which of course led to LA getting hit with the nerf bat. So was Doublefrost really over the top or was Danlitus just over the top because of his buff bot? Every Mid on Galahad is screaming for nerfs to infiltrators because they are all using buff bots and routinely mow down level 50 tanks.<br>
<br>
This is the problem with this game. Buff bots skew results. People then use those skewed results to petition for their particular agenda (example, nerfing LA and doublefrost). Then all of those effected by the change stand there completely miffed and pissed off that (1) they could never get those numbers with that particular skill (example doublefrost) and (2) now want to be fixed or have someone else nerfed (example infiltrators and dragonfang).<br>
<br>
