You and quite a few others keep making the point that Infiltrators got Shadowblades nerfed.  I've not really responded to that because I felt bad for you that you got nerfed at all, but I'm really tired of it.  There were quite a few of us who asked specifically for SBs not to be nerfed, so every time I read your generalization it irks me.<br>
<br>
What got Shadowblades nerfed was that they were able to hit pretty much any class so hard (probably very often buffed all to hell) that they one-shotted a GREAT deal more than Infiltrators or Nightshades did.  This led to a lot of battles where Albion and Hibernian forces saw people falling dead at their elbows and not seeing corresponding losses on the Midgard side.  What people didn't see was the buffs, and the fact that many targets were those that were injured or rez sick.  They didn't see that ANYONE would hit for max damage on somone sitting (remember this was pre-epic armor).  They didn't see that Slash has a bonus against the armor types of SBs primary targets.  Even when these things were pointed out, people just refused to listen.<br>
<br>
There were a lot of people calling for SB nerfs, and though jealous Infiltrators were in their ranks, those Infiltrators were surely not the majority of the nerf crusade.  Futhermore, I think they were in the minority in the Infiltrator community.  Inevitably, whines are louder than the calls for people to stop whining, so guess what happened...nerf.<br>
<br>
If you want to blame people for nerfs, I understand, but don't just blame &quot;Infiltrators.&quot;  It wasn't just us, and it wasn't most of us.<br>
<br>
Peace <p>-Aurra Sing-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umithar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mithar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/22/02 11:28:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3781.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> buffbots</span><hr size=1> amen Sing amen <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubaym.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Baym</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/22/02 11:34:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3781.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Sorry bro, but on these boards it was the infiltrators. Go read the posts again and who the posters were.<br>
